      <scopecontent id="aspace_41010e605c5476910e660a67b763b64b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This finding aid encompasses accessions of single manuscripts and small groups of manuscripts and other papers, by or pertaining to Marie Corelli, acquired by the library from a variety of sources. Materials incorporated into the collection prior to February 1998 have been organized into three series: <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref10">Series I, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Ray Livingston Murphy Bequest</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref32">Series II, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Charles J. Levy Gift</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, and <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref40">Series III, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Materials from Other Sources</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, which consists of material acquired from various other sources.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
